研究 / 教育用途声明

This repository contains Minecraft client source code recovered via MCP (Mod Coder Pack)
decompilation, together with runtime libraries and native binaries from the vanilla
Minecraft distribution.

NO OWNERSHIP CLAIM.
Minecraft, its code, assets, libraries, and native binaries are the property of
Mojang AB / Microsoft Corporation and/or their respective rights holders. The maintainer
of this repository claims NO ownership or copyright over any Minecraft / Mojang material
contained here, and grants no rights to it.

PERMITTED USE.
This material is published solely for personal education, reverse-engineering research,
debugging, and interoperability study. You must own a valid, licensed copy of Minecraft.

PROHIBITED USE.
- Any use that violates the Minecraft EULA, the Mojang/Microsoft Terms of Service, or
  applicable law.
- Distributing, reproducing, or using this to provide pirated Minecraft or to bypass,
  replace, or circumvent Minecraft's authentication / online license verification
  (e.g. authlib / Mojang/Microsoft account validation).
- Cheating against online services, malware delivery, or service disruption.

NO WARRANTY.
Provided "AS IS", without warranty of any kind. The maintainer accepts no liability for
any use or misuse.

TAKEDOWN.
If you are a rights holder (including Mojang/Microsoft) and believe any content here
infringes your rights, open an issue or contact the maintainer for prompt removal.

